{"tid":422620,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[PS4][FIFA 18 FUT]想搞個聯賽, 有冇巴打有興趣?","createTime":"2017-10-03T08:23:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-04T07:59:39.000Z","uid":25950,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"5fc6f9951c87da6eceda2115bdb35dcab36df50e","tid":422620,"uid":25950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T08:23:41.000Z","msg":"之前喺舊登有搞過一次FIFA聯賽<br />\n幾年前冇乜經驗搞得唔好爛尾, 先同有份參加過嘅巴打講聲對唔住<br />\n<br />\n吸收咗上次經驗, 咁啱FIFA18推出, 藉住呢個機會想搞多一次, 唔知有冇巴打有興趣?<br />\n<br />\n不過今次唔搞普通球隊Friendly, 轉玩FUT大家點睇?<br />\n<br />\n比賽細節等大家報咗名再公佈<br />\n暫時我諗咗幾點:<br />\n1. 單循環<br />\n2. 有升降班制度<br />\n3. FUT online Friendly<br />\n4. 唔準用training card<br />\n5. 一個星期大約打4-5場<br />\n6. 大約10個人一組, 兩個星期就完一季<br />\n<br />\n大家有咩意見可以話我聽, 我會盡量配合大家, 希望搞個好玩同埋持續性高嘅聯賽, 等大家喺打daily champ, weekend league 同 squad battle之餘, 多樣野玩下, 曬下卡又試下自己實力<br />\n<br />\n如果大家有興趣, 可以填咗下面張form, 我睇下有幾多人報名再決定分幾多組<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e442f3685f2eff5fbeef6c09d8457333d42b360","tid":422620,"uid":25950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T08:24:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa27045e966e1f8747917c2271e1664a312fee25","tid":422620,"uid":25950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T08:26:30.000Z","msg":"暫時未有限定幾多人, 不過先到先得, 根據上次經驗, 我應該可以應付到大約50人<br />\n想參加嘅巴打記得填咗form先<br />\n我收齊報名表會聯絡返你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同埋報咗名嘅留個言話聲我知, 順便推下post"},{"pid":"2531f43de6cb2f2e77ebfbe5a7af9bb384fed2a5","tid":422620,"uid":25950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T08:28:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23495d2595f676cc431e7e49acc2a063290feb7d","tid":422620,"uid":25950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T08:34:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5d9a0f71080a0c11ece68aba832a4ff91cc34f9","tid":422620,"uid":25935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T08:40:13.000Z","msg":"正評比巴打個心"},{"pid":"48b6bacb7cbd30dedfe366c37ab84cf464c1c59a","tid":422620,"uid":21279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T08:47:27.000Z","msg":"加油<br />\nBtw留名睇互屌"},{"pid":"1c5a89589141c7e37cee3af7bd660023b608be89","tid":422620,"uid":25950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T08:48:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>加油<br />\nBtw留名睇互屌</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點解會互屌"},{"pid":"f938deb4e5b0dac439052d5ba12a4b115ab3b899","tid":422620,"uid":19834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T08:53:46.000Z","msg":"明星隊尾機喎"},{"pid":"8979bfc4f83344bc90d4fd0957d7854bf74572e3","tid":422620,"uid":71712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T08:54:07.000Z","msg":"搞pro club好過"},{"pid":"b1f10a2a933212a4e1b67a68cca64ab0df49f589","tid":422620,"uid":3352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T09:41:59.000Z","msg":"已填 支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c8f952a83602c80d42330a6c58ee160d1d58a88","tid":422620,"uid":71230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T11:36:37.000Z","msg":"已留<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e69c8fb32226437135187875111d1cf04d791e2e","tid":422620,"uid":3363,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T11:46:27.000Z","msg":"冇固定既打機時間<br />\n想參加都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8018327e3dff47a16bd5f209740641b37a30b13","tid":422620,"uid":2461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0